- End of May: McGwire: 27, Sosa: 20
- End of June: McGwire: 37, Sosa: 40
- End of July: McGwire: 45, Sosa: 49
- End of August: McGwire: 55, Sosa: 62
- End of September: McGwire: 70, Sosa: 73

